<a name="Astington & Gopnik"></a><b>Astington, Janet W. and Alison Gopnik. Developing 
understanding of desire and intention</b>. <a href="#top">Whiten (1991)</a>, pp. 
39-50. 
<p>
Abstract: (summarized) Discusses the development of the understanding of belief, 
desire, and intention in childhood. (from the chapter) distinguishing desires 
and outcomes; representational nature of desire. 
